<h4>
    Rounding to a Whole Number
</h4>
<ul>
    <li>
        Look at the first decimal digit:
    </li>
    <li>
        If it is 0, 1, 2, 3, or 4, round down.
        Keep the number you have without the decimal.
    </li>
    <li>
        If it is 5, 6, 7, 8, or 9, round up.
        Move up one number and don't write the decimal.
    </li>
</ul>

