<h4>
    Rounding Negative Numbers
</h4>

<ul>
    <li>
        Look at the first decimal place
    </li>
    <li>
        If the digit is 0, 1, 2, 3, or 4: round UP.
    </li>
    <li>
        If the digit is 5, 6, 7, 8, or 9: round DOWN.
        You will have a negative number with greater magnitude.
    </li>
</ul>

